{"tid":1698890,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人老左,對拍拖睇法唔同哂","createTime":"2019-11-07T22:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T01:31:04.000Z","uid":86689,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d224261c2d2a04ceb0444ec82a3a0ac1745afcbe","tid":1698890,"uid":86689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T22:59:31.000Z","msg":"以前細個覺得揀女唔使睇外表<br />\n因為老左個個都樣衰架啦<br />\n所以要揀啲性格夾有實力有內涵的<br />\n<br />\n經過年月的洗擦,自己無論外在內在客觀主觀方面的成就/價值越來越高<br />\n慢慢就發覺遇唔撚到一啲可以同自己咁高咁大甚至勁過自己,自己能夠真心佩服的女<br />\n當追求唔到內在美,就唯有專追外在算了<br />\n<br />\n另一方面經歷多左,見識到真係有啲女外表係不堪到超越年歲的法則<br />\n再睇多啲例子反省返,發現本身樣靚身材FIT的,老左都會KEEP到,唔係人人老左都樣衰的<br />\n<br />\n而家如果拖一個唔係白滑高瘦的女出街甚至會覺得好無面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4208e9b72bbb1a0f22a09e0b57111151e203bbc1","tid":1698890,"uid":115660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"自大毒撚真係好可怕"},{"pid":"f88fbf8bd6e37d7317fa02f63f5a24e042f9290a","tid":1698890,"uid":138981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:52:16.000Z","msg":"有幾咁高咁大呀你"},{"pid":"46a366404619fe2a557815b23cf2d85b8a709c6d","tid":1698890,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"連登又多返呢d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果然係連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60fe1ae2440e72d7f93eee61d2969944bdbc689","tid":1698890,"uid":86689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46a366404619fe2a557815b23cf2d85b8a709c6d","tid":1698890,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"連登又多返呢d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果然係連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:31:04.000Z","msg":"真係出去果啲就知連登唔可靠啦<br />\n唔好當連登係大台,連登啲內容啱用咪用,唔啱用好正常"}]}